  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coldridge is a push-your-luck board game: Explore and Exploit, with  gambling and roguelike mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GOLD RUSH: HIGH RISK, HIGH REWARD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick  contracts, go out and prospect for rare resources. The riskier the contract, the juicier the reward but the harder the fall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREAK THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the best synergies with over 50+ items and 4 characters to play. There's always a new build available to beat your high score<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/d25f1a3c6b82b921550887a5e387929a.avif?t=1769676114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras_big/d25f1a3c6b82b921550887a5e387929a.avif?t=1769676114 width=800 height=394 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOARD GAME MECHANICS AND  MOVEMENT PLANNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fulfill your contracts by meticulously planning your moves. Utilize the terrain and your equipment to gain an edge, outmaneuver obstacles, and complete your objectives efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSPIRATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coldridge takes inspiration from games like Catan, Dorfromantik, Carcassonne, Wingspan, or Ticket To Ride. We're huge board game fans, but also Rogue-lite and Soulslike games fans</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coldridge is a push-your-luck board game: Explore and Exploit, with  gambling and roguelike mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GOLD RUSH: HIGH RISK, HIGH REWARD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick  contracts, go out and prospect for rare resources. The riskier the contract, the juicier the reward but the harder the fall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREAK THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the best synergies with over 50+ items and 4 characters to play. There's always a new build available to beat your high score<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/d25f1a3c6b82b921550887a5e387929a.avif?t=1769676114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras_big/d25f1a3c6b82b921550887a5e387929a.avif?t=1769676114 width=800 height=394 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOARD GAME MECHANICS AND  MOVEMENT PLANNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fulfill your contracts by meticulously planning your moves. Utilize the terrain and your equipment to gain an edge, outmaneuver obstacles, and complete your objectives efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSPIRATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coldridge takes inspiration from games like Catan, Dorfromantik, Carcassonne, Wingspan, or Ticket To Ride. We're huge board game fans, but also Rogue-lite and Soulslike games fans</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
